Lines.Comment: Do not record.
Subtle, not overt
This world will burn with our coming.
Come brother, our victory awaits.
Lend me your power, brother.
You lead us only to failure, brother! I make my own way.
We must take this world for our own.
You will find that I am not easily impressed.
Can you put aside our differences and fight, demon?
Your words seep with poison and lies.
Can you put aside our differences long enough for us to ensure victory, demon?
Hatred is a concern of the living.
Let us say for now we have struck a bargain.
Ah, the lord of hatred. I've heard much about you demon.
Ah, ah, ah... flattery will get you nowhere.
The Lord of Hatred. Very impressive, I'm sure.
There is no greater hatred and scorn than that which exists in my heart!
Are you a demon, or undead? Hmph. I'll just have to hate you twice as much.
I assure you, the feeling is mutual.
Well met, friend.
Let our enemy be shattered upon our resolve!
Organism Abathur will not fail. Victory assured.
Creature recognized. Good sequences. Survival, likely.
We are allied for now, but I will not allow your foul magics to pollute this realm when this is over.
I loath to ally with demons. But it cannot be helped.
Do you know how many of your kind have been impaled on my javelin?
Stay out of my way, demon, and you may live through this.
Yes, it is me. And once again, I will find a way to defeat you.
I would rather die than fight for you.
You are strong. Will bring much essence.
Silence, demon, or I'll bury gorehowl in your skull.
My fate is my own, demon!
